data.description:
Nestled in the welcoming neighborhood of Horizon at Towne Meadow in Aurora, Colorado, this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-story home at 4336 S Kellispell Cir is a true gem that offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.

As you step inside, you'll be immediately struck by the well-lit and spacious open layout. The seamless connection between the living, dining, and kitchen areas create an inviting atmosphere that's perfect for daily life and gatherings. Whether you're preparing a meal in the kitchen, enjoying a family dinner in the dining area, or unwinding in the living room, this open floor plan ensures you'll never miss a moment with your loved ones.

The modern kitchen, undoubtedly the heart of this home, offers a spacius practical workspace. You'll find ample storage space to keep your kitchen organized and clutter-free and a pantery to store all your culinary essentials.

Five generously sized bedrooms can comfortably accommodate your family. The master suite is a true retreat within the home. It features a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom that's reminiscent of a spa. The bathroom includes a luxurious soaking tub and a separate shower, offering you a sanctuary to unwind and rejuvenate after a long day.

 This outdoor space is a versatile extension of your home and is a great place to create lasting memories with family and friends.

One of the standout features of this property is its prime location. You'll be living in a friendly neighborhood that offers easy access to parks, schools, shopping, and dining. Major highways are also conveniently nearby, making your daily commute a breeze. Everything you need is within a short distance, from everyday conveniences to recreational activities.

Schedule a viewing today and see for yourself. For more details and to arrange a visit, please contact John McComas at 303-668-5542. Your dream home awaits in beautiful Aurora, Colorado.
